  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'God, you\'re awful. And you don\'t know how awful you\'re.',
  author: 'Will Gardner (The Good Wife)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'I refuse to be a failure. I don\'t care what you want anymore. This is how it\'s going to work : You will be here only when I tell you to be here. I\'m drawing a 50 mile radius around this house and if you so much as open your fly to urinate, I will destoy you.',
