}, {
  quote: 'It’s a shame you can only die once.',
  author: 'Dexter Morgan (Dexter)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'Pain or damage don\'t end the world. Or despair, or f*cking beatings. The world ends when you\'re dead. Until then, you got more punishment in store. Stand it like a man ... and give some back.',
  author: 'Al Swearengen (Deadwood)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'A Lannister always pays his debts.',
  author: 'Lannister house motto (Game of thrones)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'I’m not in the meth business. I’m in the empire business.',
  author: 'Walter White (Breaking Bad)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'But a true champion, face to face with his darkest hour, will do whatever it takes to rise above. A man fights, and fights and then fights some more. Because surrender is death, and death is for pussies.',
  author: 'Kenny Powers (Eastbound & Down)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'I’ll kill a man in a fair fight... or if I think he’s gonna start a fair fight.',
  author: 'Jayne Cobb (Firefly)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'Here’s my counter-offer to your counter-offer: Go f*ck yourself.',
  author: 'Al Swearengen (Deadwood)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'Capitalism: God’s way of determining who is smart and who is poor.',
  author: 'Ron Swanson (Parks and recreation)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'How you expect to run with the wolves come night, when you spend all day sparrin’ with the puppies?',
  author: 'Omar Little (The Wire)',
  link: '#'
}, {
  quote: 'What use is an unloaded gun?',
